name: ITLibMediaItemPlayStatus
desc: These constants specify the play status of the media item.

items.name: case none
items.desc: The user has played the media item or iTunes doesn’t track the play status for this kind of media item.

items.name: case partiallyPlayed
items.desc: The user has partially played the media item.

items.name: case unplayed
items.desc: The user hasn’t played the media item.
